CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.TagInventoryTrackingHistory`
(
  TagInventoryTrackingHistoryId STRING NOT NULL,
  TagInventoryTrackingId STRING NOT NULL,
  InventoryLocationId STRING NOT NULL,
  PriorInventoryLocationId STRING,
  TagStatusId STRING NOT NULL,
  PriorTagStatusId STRING,
  DatetimeChanged TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DatetimeChanged)
CLUSTER BY TagInventoryTrackingId, TagStatusId;
